name: This Youtuber Does Not Exist
description:
If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

VAE Not required - but can produce extra oomph if desired!
Trained on stock photos, youtubers portraits.

This was casually intended to be a MEME, but it somehow came out to be a really good portrait model.

The meme factor is:

  • Try adding in "MARKIPLIER"

  • Try adding in ARIN HANSON

  • TRY ADDING IN DAN AVIDAN

Cause ya won't get them EXACTLY, you might get Eef & ARin's futuristic baby but that's about it XD
